Package: qboost
Type: Package
Title: Quantile Gradient Boosting Models
Version: 0.5.1
Authors@R:
    person("Cassio", "Pagnoncelli", , "cassiopagnoncelli@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0000-7114-7008"))
Description: Quantile regression suite using LightGBM gradient boosting. 
    'qboost()' fits standard quantile regression with cross-validation and 
    early stopping. 'qtail()' models extreme quantiles via stacked architecture: 
    ensemble of qboost base learners combined through elastic net, extended to 
    tail region using Generalized Pareto Distribution from Extreme Value Theory. 
    'qevt()' detects extreme events using threshold exceedance models and GPD. 
    Includes calibration diagnostics (coverage, QCE, PIT), PAVA monotonicity 
    enforcement, formula and matrix interfaces, and S3 methods.
